{"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/showsuserlocation"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"assign"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"showsUserLocation"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Setting this property to "},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" causes the map view to use the Core Location"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"framework to find the current location. As long as this property is "},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map view continues to track the user’s location and update it periodically."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This property does not indicate whether the user’s position is actually visible","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"on the map, only whether the map view is allowed to display it. To determine","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"whether the user’s position is visible, use the ","type":"text"},{"code":"userLocationVisible","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The default value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Your app must specify a value for ","type":"text"},{"code":"NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"NSLocationAlwaysUsageDescription","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" in its ","type":"text"},{"code":"Info.plist","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to satisfy the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"requirements of the underlying Core Location framework when enabling this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you implement a custom location manager, set the "},{"code":"locationManager","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" before"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"calling "},{"code":"showsUserLocation","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/showsUserLocation","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"showsUserLocation"}],"title":"showsUserLocation","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)showsUserLocation","symbolKind":"property","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L590"},"roleHeading":"Instance Property","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"showsUserLocation"}]},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value indicating whether the map may display the user location."}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/showsUserLocation":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value indicating whether the map may display the user location."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/